Title: Littmann Classic III 5803 Acoutic Stethoscope(Black)
Description: The 3M™ Littmann® Classic III™ Stethoscope is the latest version of the stethoscope that helps millions of medical professionals achieve their best. The Classic III stethoscope offers high acoustic sensitivity for exceptional performance, plus a versatile two-sided chestpiece with tunable diaphragms. The Classic III stethoscope is used by students and medical professionals alike to identify, listen to, and study heart, lung, and other body sounds for physical assessment, patient monitoring, and diagnosis. Tunable diaphragm technology—a 3M invention—lets clinicians hear different frequency sounds by simply adjusting the pressure on the chestpiece. Hold the chestpiece with light pressure to hear low frequency sounds; press a little more to hear higher frequency sounds. This time-saving feature allows the healthcare provider to focus on the patient, while the non-chill diaphragm provides patient comfort. Headset tension is easily adjusted for head size and comfort by squeezing together or pulling apart the eartubes. Snap-tight, soft-sealing eartips conform to individual ears for an excellent acoustic seal and comfortable fit. Eartips snap firmly onto the ends of the eartubes and, for safety, require a significant effort to remove. Resilient next-generation tubing retains its shape and flexibility even after folding tightly into a pocket. It provides longer stethoscope life due to improved resistance to skin oils and alcohol, and is less likely to pick up stains. Next-generation tubing is not made with natural rubber latex, a benefit to sensitive medical professionals and their patients. And, to play its part in the protection of human health and the environment, the next-generation tubing does not contain phthalate plasticizers. The Classic III stethoscope is made in the USA for consistent quality. It comes complete with large and small soft-sealing eartips, non-chill bell sleeve, and instructions.

Title: Oriflame Sweden Beauty 2FX 8 ml(Black)
Description: Introducing the revolutionary 2FX Mascara - one mascara, two effects. For the first time, you can give your eyes two amazing looks - highly defined, separated and longer lashes or fuller, volumised lashes - all from a single innovative applicator thanks to a breakthrough in mascara technology. The innovation is in the ingenious cap and clever adjustable bristle brush which can be changed to suit your needs and style. If you open one cap, you have a thin brush with a small amount of formula which gives your lashes a light coat of mascara, separating, defining and lengthening them. And with a simple twist and click, you can open the other cap and you suddenly have a thicker ultra volume brush, with more formula to create volumised, fuller lashes - truly eye catching! Clinically tested, Oriflame's 2FX mascara makes your lashes up to 40% longer and creates nine times more volume. 91%* of women who have tried 2FX believe it is easy to use and delivers two very distinct mascara results. And what's more, its longer wearing formula means you don't have to re-apply! *Based on consumer self-assessment on 99 women Length or volume: 2 effects in 1 mascara. Whatever your mission, get lashes to match. Directions: One mascara, Two effects - How does it all work? While it might at first appear that there are two different brushes, there is of course only one. Thanks to an innovative brush wiper mechanism, opening the black cap limits the amount of bulk that is deposited on the brush for defined yet lengthened lashes. When you open the silver cap more mascara is left on the brush for voluptuous and volumized lashes. 2FX mascara is a secret beauty weapon in your hand bag!
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Makeup>Eyes>Mascaras
